# subscriberNumber()

**Instance Method**

Requests that the Bluetooth audio gateway send the subscriber number to the delegate.

## Declaration

```swift
func subscriberNumber()
```

## Discussion

The subscriber number is sent to the [doc://com.apple.iobluetooth/documentation/IOBluetooth/IOBluetoothHandsFreeDeviceDelegate/handsFree(_:subscriberNumber:)] function of the delegate.

## Requesting Status Information

- **currentCallList()**: Requests that the Bluetooth audio gateway send the delegate a list of calls that are active, on hold, or being set up.
